longBusinessSummary: Shareholder Value Beteiligungen AG is a publicly owned investment manager. The firm provides its services to Institutional and private investors. It also manages various funds. The firm invests in europe-wide small cap stocks markets of German-speaking region. Shareholder Value Beteiligungen AG was founded in 1999 and is based in Frankfurt, Germany.
